title: John Maindonald
text:
For the website for “A Practical Guide to Data Analysis Using R …” (John Maindonald with coauthors John Braun and Jeffrey Andrews, CUP 2024), go to
https://jhmaindonald.github.io/PGRcode/.
Additionally, links are likely to be added, in due course, for web pages relevant to John Maindonald’s life, work, and involvements.
